# MailChimp Integration Standards

## API Implementation
- Use official MailChimp API client libraries
- Implement proper API key management and security
- Apply rate limiting and quota management
- Handle API errors with appropriate retry logic
- Log API interactions for troubleshooting
- Document API version dependencies

## Data Synchronization
- Implement reliable user data synchronization
- Apply proper field mapping for user attributes
- Handle merges and updates consistently
- Implement batch operations for efficiency
- Create audit logs for synchronization activities
- Validate data integrity after synchronization

## Behavioral Trigger Automation
- Implement onboarding email sequences for new users
- Create re-engagement campaigns for inactive subscribers
- Apply cart abandonment and feature usage triggers
- Implement lifecycle-based communication flows
- Create win-back campaigns for churned users
- Document automation trigger logic and timing

## Template Management
- Implement version control for email templates
- Apply testing procedures for template updates
- Create reusable template components
- Document template structure and variables
- Implement preview and testing workflows
- Apply proper template deployment processes

